Class
	tnbLib::hPowerThermo

Description
	Power-function based thermodynamics package templated on EquationOfState.

	In this thermodynamics package the heat capacity is a simple power of
	temperature:

		Cp(T) = c0*(T/Tref)^n0;

	which is particularly suitable for solids.

